{"id": "1438963000009822281", "channel_id": "1385040039448412170", "type": 0, "author_id": "1280986327659188334", "author_name": "cometovilla", "author_bot": false, "content": "We've said several times that the server will be changed , which includes the removal of objectionable phrases. \n\nWe decided to impose a filter on the majority of swear words to provide a safe and welcoming atmosphere for people of all ages, in keeping with our goal of maintaining a family-friendly space.  \n\nAn automated moderation bot (or Discord's AutoMod tool) was used to delete messages that included prohibited words.  The filter was activated to make it easier for us to enforce this new community standard.", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T18:45:13.842000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
